      • amqpTaskPublish

        public void amqpTaskPublish(Task task,
                   String exchangeName,
                   String eventName,
                   String taskId)
        Publishes a message to amqp that describes what action a user has just performed on a task. These actions may be either TaskTaken or TaskCompleted. This calls checkInitialized to see if there is a valid connection to qpid.
        Parameters:
        task - the task that has been acted upon
        exchangeName - the exchange name for messaging
        eventName - the event that correlates with the action
        taskId - the id of the task that was acted upon
